{"tid":1078033,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"原來貓夜晚真係會想殺死人類","createTime":"2019-03-26T04:14:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T02:23:47.000Z","uid":44569,"like":104,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"0bcf0b75f46a4320664746f6e7b64ff574408cca","tid":1078033,"uid":44569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T04:14:14.000Z","msg":"作為貓奴應該好想知每晚自己瞓咗覺之後，隻貓究竟做緊啲咩？泰國有位貓奴決定裝個鏡頭偷拍吓，由於啲相太搞笑，佢放咗上Facebook群組Love Cat Club之後好多人分享。睇相見隻貓會眼定定望實佢(似乎怕佢暈咗？)、又會坐喺佢塊臉上面，有時就責住佢心口瞓，唔知佢會唔會每晚發惡夢？不過網民就話睇得出隻貓好鍾意主人，作為貓奴，今晚有無心思思想裝返個cam？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.gameover.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/25084348/ca122-600x446.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.gameover.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F25084348%2Fca122-600x446.jpg&h=0c3066a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.gameover.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/25084212/ca110-600x326.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.gameover.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F25084212%2Fca110-600x326.jpg&h=c4d5bb5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.gameover.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/25084232/ca214-600x313.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.gameover.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F25084232%2Fca214-600x313.jpg&h=6699cbf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.gameover.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/25084243/ca34-600x327.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.gameover.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F25084243%2Fca34-600x327.jpg&h=b1143ab6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.gameover.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/25084251/ca42-600x253.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.gameover.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F25084251%2Fca42-600x253.jpg&h=3e1242a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.gameover.com.hk/wp-content/uploads